      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_10" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">35.017-3</ph> Using an FFRDC.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d2256e13">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2270e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  All work placed with the FFRDC must be within the purpose, mission, general scope of effort, or special competency of the FFRDC.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d2270e26" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  Where the use of the FFRDC by a nonsponsor is permitted by the sponsor, the sponsor shall be responsible for compliance with paragraph (a) of this subsection.</p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d2256e32">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2270e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        The nonsponsoring agency shall prepare a determination in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1102811.dita#i1102811"
                              base="i1102811"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">17.502-1</xref>(a) and provide the documentation required by <xref href="FAR-i1102872.dita#i1102872"
                              base="i1102872"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">17.503</xref>(e) to the sponsoring agency.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2270e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        When a D&amp;F is required pursuant to <xref href="FAR-i1102847.dita#i1102847"
                              base="i1102847"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">17.502-2</xref>(c), the nonsponsoring agency may incorporate the determination required by <xref href="FAR-i1102811.dita#i1102811"
                              base="i1102811"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">17.502-1</xref>(a) into the D&amp;F and provide the documentation required by <xref href="FAR-i1102872.dita#i1102872"
                              base="i1102872"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">17.503</xref>(e) to the sponsoring agency.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d2270e69" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        When permitted by the sponsor, a Federal agency may contract directly with the FFRDC, in which case that Federal agency is responsible for compliance with part <xref href="FAR-i1120119.dita#i1120119"
                              base="i1120119"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">6</xref>.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
